name: Im Blessed And I Know That I Am
chorusText:
I’m blessed

I’m blessed and I know that I am
since Jesus took control of my life
I’m blessed and I know that I am
for He promise to me a new life
I’m blessed because He walks with me
and He leads me where ever I go
and if it happens that you ask me
howare you my friend
I’m blessed, I’m blessed, I’m blessed
